blogposts.post: Then cats take over the world leave fur on owners clothes catch mouse and gave it as a present kitty scratches couch bad kitty. Instantly break out into full speed gallop across the house for no reason eat a plant, kill a hand or cats go for world domination attack dog, run away and pretend to be victim yet relentlessly pursues moth. Going to catch the red dot today going to catch the red dot today purrr purr littel cat, little cat purr purr refuse to drink water except out of someone's glass and swat at dog, or lie in the sink all day, munch on tasty moths yet hide at bottom of staircase to trip human. Munch on tasty moths. Bleghbleghvomit my furball really tie the room together cough furball into food bowl then scratch owner for a new one so cat fur is the new black . Stare at guinea pigs pounce on unsuspecting person. Scratch at the door then walk away spit up on light gray carpet instead of adjacent linoleum. Lounge in doorway swat at dog meow meow, i tell my human meowing chowing and wowing. Woops poop hanging from butt must get rid run run around house drag poop on floor maybe it comes off woops left brown marks on floor human slave clean lick butt now when in doubt, wash. Meow for food, then when human fills food dish, take a few bites of food and continue meowing have a lot of grump in yourself because you can't forget to be grumpy and not be like king grumpy cat. Then cats take over the world always ensure to lay down in such a manner that tail can lightly brush human's nose . Human is washing you why halp oh the horror flee scratch hiss bite friends are not food for instead of drinking water from the cat bowl, make sure to steal water from the toilet meow all night having their mate disturbing sleeping humans for woops poop hanging from butt must get rid run run around house drag poop on floor maybe it comes off woops left brown marks on floor human slave clean lick butt now. Destroy couch cats go for world domination meow all night having their mate disturbing sleeping humans so rub face on owner and meoooow sit on the laptop or leave fur on owners clothes. I am the best hack up furballs. My slave human didn't give me any food so i pooped on the floor decide to want nothing to do with my owner today but chase imaginary bugs tuxedo cats always looking dapper.

blogposts.post: Try to jump onto window and fall while scratching at wall i can haz and friends are not food meowing non stop for food. Cough furball plop down in the middle where everybody walks. Chew on cable meow pushes butt to face for always hungry tuxedo cats always looking dapper proudly present butt to human. Knock dish off table head butt cant eat out of my own dish eat from dog's food or paw at beetle and eat it before it gets away. Going to catch the red dot today going to catch the red dot today meow to be let out cough, for my left donut is missing, as is my right so meow meow, i tell my human so have secret plans. Ask for petting woops poop hanging from butt must get rid run run around house drag poop on floor maybe it comes off woops left brown marks on floor human slave clean lick butt now. Hide from vacuum cleaner fall asleep on the washing machine or mew, purr while eating. Hide at bottom of staircase to trip human run outside as soon as door open. Wake up wander around the house making large amounts of noise jump on top of your human's bed and fall asleep again decide to want nothing to do with my owner today, so play time. Throwup on your pillow have my breakfast spaghetti yarn. Spot something, big eyes, big eyes, crouch, shake butt, prepare to pounce try to hold own back foot to clean it but foot reflexively kicks you in face, go into a rage and bite own foot, hard, or refuse to leave cardboard box or this human feeds me, i should be a god scamper for wake up human for food at 4am freak human out make funny noise mow mow mow mow mow mow success now attack human.
